      • attachRangeCounts

        protected void attachRangeCounts(AST2BOpContext ctx,
                                 List<StatementPatternNode> spNodes,
                                 IBindingSet exogenousBindings)
        Use the SPORelation from the database to grab the appropriate range counts for the StatementPatternNodes. Only tries to attach them if the annotation AST2BOpBase.Annotations.ESTIMATED_CARDINALITY is not already attached to the node. This makes it possible to write unit tests without real data.
